      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lamb mixture</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and evenly top with the<strong> mashed potato</strong></p><p>Tip: Gently run a fork over the mash to create a crispy top!</p><p>Put the dish in the oven for 15-20 min or until golden brown and bubbling – this is your <strong>shepherd's pie</strong></p>",
